    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
      <p>Glasgow writes regarding her personal life and financial
         difficulties during the Great Depression. Also included is a
         poem by Glasgow dated France, 1916; and a typescript citation
         of Glasgow, 1930 June 10, by H.W. Chase, University of North
         Carolina.</p>
    </scopecontent>
    <arrangement>
      <head>Arrangement</head>
      <p>The letters are arranged chronologically.</p>
    </arrangement>
